{"tid":2148192,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"一日兩事故　深航急降5,500米","createTime":"2020-08-09T18:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-10T04:37:36.000Z","uid":240362,"like":153,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"a4404a7dd0f9f72f4bc0084954dfe3f0507885e0","tid":2148192,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T18:58:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200810/DWFQF3HGJ22BDJ6G766DTNKB3E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200810%2FDWFQF3HGJ22BDJ6G766DTNKB3E%2F&d=V6cANorTbu7KkBEK5B25Yiukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=8c3efa17\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200810%2FDWFQF3HGJ22BDJ6G766DTNKB3E%2F&h=e2f179ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200810/DWFQF3HGJ22BDJ6G766DTNKB3E/</a><br />\n<br />\n中國短短十小時內發生兩宗航空事故，深圳航空及東方航空昨分別有航班因機械故障需要緊急折返或急降其他機場，深航客機五分鐘內急降5,500米，一度發出緊急代碼。中國一天內接連發生兩宗航空事故，網民高度關注：「一天之內，兩起故障，從深航到東航，甚麽情况？」"},{"pid":"51407a7ecad61b77f2a780ea7d8909099cef3c5f","tid":2148192,"uid":9193,"like":32,"dislike":2,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T19:00:17.000Z","msg":"鬼國不意外"},{"pid":"77ef9a9d20de28bf5bd7bbaa3da857df1bb100f6","tid":2148192,"uid":49955,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T19:00:25.000Z","msg":"見到深圳兩個字就知咩料啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64b729f6458bdca2f50e68c72eb9647235d07e03","tid":2148192,"uid":95519,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T19:01:24.000Z","msg":"係咪裝左個北斗出事"},{"pid":"4d46143d2c47b9f3c1131fdb669ef7195b39d2b0","tid":2148192,"uid":253608,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T19:02:59.000Z","msg":"沒事兒"},{"pid":"38333b22f1400a1cdcfcbbdacc35ff5b6e9a91af","tid":2148192,"uid":53026,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-10T00:25:25.000Z","msg":"起你老母！"},{"pid":"f81127daeccc8f28e10fa